{"tid":237700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「寸嘴巴塞仔」旺角7-11偷竊 「偷少少野啫」","createTime":"2017-05-10T14:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T15:21:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b071d575d493783da098e27341e32d89b59cc211","tid":237700,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"星島日報\t星島日報2017年5月10日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/55Hj77RanbrQA9.hDk3U0A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170510a083025.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F55Hj77RanbrQA9.hDk3U0A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170510a083025.jpg&h=0fadaf82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】外籍青年今晨在旺角便利店高買，事後還「得戚」向警員示烕，表示自己只是「偷少少野」，認為不用拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n今晨約1時24分，被捕的28歲外籍青年，身穿巴塞隆拿球衣，在旺角亞皆老街8號7-Eleven便利店，懷疑偷去一瓶防曬噴劑、一盒防蚊貼、一支紅酒及三瓶維他命丸，總值約430元，在角落將物品放進背囊，不過店員一早識破，經過閉路電視翻查，即使他準備離開，亦無藉口離開，53歲職員隨即報警。<br />\n<br />\n但保安員及警員到場，這名身穿巴塞隆拿球衣的男子，未能出示身份證明文件，並當場在他背囊發現該批物品，但查問期間，巴塞仔「寸嘴」表示只是「偷少少野」，又問「咁小事拉我？」。男子涉嫌盜竊及未能出示身份證明文件被捕。案件交由旺角警區刑事調查第六隊跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%B8%E5%98%B4%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E4%BB%94-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%927-11%E5%81%B7%E7%AB%8A-%E5%81%B7%E5%B0%91%E5%B0%91%E9%87%8E%E5%95%AB-002700512.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25B8%25E5%2598%25B4%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A1%259E%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%25927-11%25E5%2581%25B7%25E7%25AB%258A-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B0%2591%25E9%2587%258E%25E5%2595%25AB-002700512.html&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TakkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a70fe466\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%B8%E5%98%B4%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E4%BB%94-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%927-11%E5%81%B7%E7%AB%8A-%E5%81%B7%E5%B0%91%E5%B0%91%E9%87%8E%E5%95%AB-002700512.html</a>"},{"pid":"8eb4d418824e0d4e5e3a0e8a32d896b5138b7e67","tid":237700,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"佢最大既罪行就係只偷小小野<br />\n<br />\n如果佢偷左成個國家番來, 佢就係開國者<br />\n<br />\n例如毛澤東"},{"pid":"a0bc17a2bd1e20bb64df693e03f4042f602b9201","tid":237700,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"外籍青年係咩國家 識廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df8909029263aa7301cae01e3c21dca2bc33398","tid":237700,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"大陸偷渡仔"},{"pid":"c2f4863cbc6d224d5591e87b92ebce34bb4f6c4c","tid":237700,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢最大既罪行就係只偷小小野<br />\n<br />\n如果佢偷左成個國家番來, 佢就係開國者<br />\n<br />\n例如毛澤東</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n豬元帥真係咩post都鳩up到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329f4fce89e21e38dce95773f59b3e1d270836ea","tid":237700,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"268b4cdff2f2b52b43c890c880a53ecfd0fe228a","tid":237700,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"南亞仔開始搞事 <br />\n繼而出現強姦打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05b3bddc65ac2d88adfc3ff07a261df4f10b32f","tid":237700,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be8feeeef23cb8582e1874701980ec8f814cab98","tid":237700,"uid":6992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"搞笑咩你，巴塞歐聯出左局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}